        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Plumatella pseudostolonata, Specimen No. 46. (a) Colony fragment on rock, scale bar = 2 mm; (b) ventral (?) floatoblast valves, modified slightly from Borg (1940) to show the fenestrae more clearly; (c) detail of sessoblast showing wide, unmarked annulus and tubercles on frontal valve, scale bar = 50 μm." ;
